        "p3",
        "p4",
        "education gradesync",
        "education contentcdn",
        "education studentdb"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，SJF非抢占式意味着短作业优先且不会中途切换。我注意到P3和P2都是Education_ContentCDN，这是同一个服务的不同实例吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "education contentcdn",
        "preemptive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，P2和P3都是ContentCDN的实例，但P2先到达。另外P4比较特殊，它既有CPU执行又有I/O操作，而且I/O完成后还会再次进入CPU。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "p4",
        "p4 io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我建议用两个section来区分：CPU和I/O。P1_IO、P4_IO、P2_IO这些关键I/O节点用crit样式标注，因为它们可能阻塞系统。时间轴用纯数字秒数，axisFormat设成%s。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "cpu",
        "io",
        "p1 io",
        "p4 io",
        "p2 io",
        "axisf",
        "datef"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，时间格式用X表示纯数字时间戳。P1(Education_GradeSync)是第一个执行的，从0开始，burst time是5秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "education gradesync",
        "datef"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，CPU section里P1已经画好了，0到5的active状态。接下来P4应该接上去？SJF的话P4的burst time是2，比P2的3和P3的4都要短。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p1",
        "p4",
        "p2",
        "p3",
        "cpu"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，P4在5时刻开始，执行到7。但要注意P4在5时刻同时会触发I/O操作，这个并发关系要体现出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "p4",
        "p4 io",
        "cpu",
        "io"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P4的CPU段画好了，5到7。同时I/O section里P1_IO从5开始到7结束，对应P1完成后触发的ContentCDN读取。P4_IO紧接着从7到10，对应LMS Portal的I/O。",
      "elements_involved": [
