    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "修正了，P4_IO的标签改成Education_LMS_Portal。那P2_IO呢？从时间上看P2在CPU执行完后，10时刻开始I/O，到11结束，对应StudentDB操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
